android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.CALL_PHONE.description: Allows the application to call phone numbers without your intervention. Malicious applications may cause unexpected calls on your phone bill. Note that this does not allow the application to call emergency numbers.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

QR Code Reader Barcode Scanner is the best QR and barcode scanner. This app is fast and work for free to scan any code in the world!

Using the phone's camera, our QR Code Reader Barcode Scanner will rapidly scan QR and identify the information of barcode with our app.

📌Feature :

1. Scan and read barcode and QR code fast by point phone's camera to code. It's auto-focus and can enable flashlight for more light.
2. Save QR code or barcode that read to image file to your gallery. Also change code's color.
3. We also provide many type of QR code generator, barcode maker, QR maker & QR reader types like personal profile, contact, message, free text, mail, website, company profile etc. Just select any of these classes and fill vital fields to barcode maker image and QR code reader
4. Open image of QR code or barcode and read it.
5. Scan history saved, can be retrieve any time
6. Share your information with your friends.

📌How to use:

1. Open the QR code scanner
2. Point the camera to the QR code/bar-code
3. Auto recognize, scan and decode
4. Get results and relevant options

If you love our app, please rate us for 5 stars ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
